# Hoist Cursor SDK platform-specific binary packages to the workspace root
# `node_modules/@cursor/sdk-<platform>-<arch>/`. The Cursor SDK auto-discovers
# the bundled `cursorsandbox` binary by walking up from `process.argv[1]`
# looking for `node_modules/@cursor/sdk-<platform>-<arch>/bin/cursorsandbox`.
# In pnpm's strict mode (the default) transitive optionalDependencies stay
# under .pnpm/ where the SDK can't find them — without this hoist, sandbox
# support silently fails. Pattern matches both the @cursor/sdk-* line of
# packages and the legacy @cursor/february-* names the SDK also probes.
public-hoist-pattern[]=@cursor/sdk-*
public-hoist-pattern[]=@cursor/february-*
